The UN proposed yesterday in Cancún a renewal plan for domestic, commercial and industrial lighting in 100 countries to achieve a reduction in greenhouse gases (GES), which corresponds to nearly one-third of the additional reduction to be achieved to stabilize the planet climate by 2020.
